node.text:
Happy Earth Day!

Thank you to everyone who shared their amazing creative suggestions with @wyliecaudillart last week. In honor of #EarthMonth, Wylie painted an incredible triple-vignette mural that will certainly impress you. Watch the entire creative process - and tell us what you think of the final reveal!

Should we invite Wylie to paint another mural? If so, comment and share your ideas!

#SHLTR #EarthDay #EarthDay2021

node.text:
Kicking off the week with another #MondayRoundup of must-read content on our website! Links to all articles mentioned can be found in our bio.

Image 1: We compiled a list of 11 stylish, luxe desks for #backtoschool and #wfh life.
Image 2: Take a peek at the new @elanbyrd Rug + Pillow Collection for @luluandgeorgia. 
Image 3: Manhattan Beached-based interior designer @lesbeaux shows us three of her outdoor spaces and shares her pro tips.
Image 4: A Q+A with John Humphreys of @humphreysbrand - his take on design and his most significant influences.

#SHLTR
